<doc id='voa_2486332' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voashona.com/a/zimbabwe-politics-health-ebola/2486332.html' term='ebola'>
Hurumende Yotsvaga Mari yeKudzivirira Ebola
WASHINGTON DC —
Gurukota rezvehutano, Doctor David Parirenyatwa, vanoti bazi ravo rinoda mari inoita mamiriyoni matatu nemazana mashanu ezviuru zvemadhora kuitira kuti rikwanise kugadzirira kurwisa chirwere chanetsa cheEbola.
Chirwere ichi chinonzi chauraya vanhu vanodarika zviuru zvina nechidimbu mudunhu reWest Africa.
Sangano reWorld Health Organisation rinotiwo chirwere ichi chiri kupararira kakapetwa kaviri mumasvondo mana oga oga.
Doctor Parirenyatwa vaudza Studio7 kuti mari iyi inenge ichizoshandiswa mukudzivirirwa kwechirwere ichi, sezvo pasi rose riri kuti chirwere ichi chinofanirwa kuparadzirwa padzinde racho, rinove nyika nhatu dzakabatwa nacho pari zvino dzinoti Guinea, Sierra Leone ne Liberia.
Vatiwo mari zhinji inenge ichizoenda kunodzidzisa vashandi vezvehutano, vashandi venzvimbo dzekupinda pamwe nekubuda kwevanhu munyika, pamwe nekutenga midziyo yakakodzera yakaita sema amburenzi nezvimwe zvekushandisa.
Doctor Parirenyatwa vanotiwo miganho yenyika inofanirwa kusimbiswa pamwe nekuchengetedzwa zvakasimba.
Vatiwo veruzhinji vanofanirwa kuwaniswa dzidziso yakasimba yechirwere cheEbola kuitira kuti vagare vachiziva nezvechirwere ichi.
Hurumende inonzi yakangopa bazi rezvehutano mari inoita zana nemakumi matatu ezviuru zvemadhora iyo inonzi yose yakaperera mukudzidzisa vashandi pamwe nezvechirwere ichi.
Veruzhinji munyika vanoti havasi kuwana ruzivo rwakakwana pamusoro pechirwere ichi nenzira dzekuti vazvidzivirire kubva kuchirwere ichi.
Boka rezvekushanyirwa kwenyika, reZimbabwe Tourism Authority, rinoti dambudziko reEbola raita kuti nyika irasikirwe nemari inodarika mamiriyoni matanhatu emadhora, sezvo vamwe vemakambani ainge ati achapinda munyika kumusangano weSangani/Hlanganani Travel Expo vakakanzura nzendo dzavo vachiti vari kutya Ebola.
Sachigaro wesangano reZimbabwe Association of Doctors for Human Rights, Amai Rutendo Bonde, vanoti zvataurwa naDoctor Parirenyatwa zvinotsinhira zvavagara vachitaura zvekuti hurumende haina kugadzirira zvakakwana.
Mukuru weManor Care, vachishanda vakazvimirira kuEngland, Doctor Brighton Chireka, vanotiwo zvimwe zvinofanirwa kuitwa nehurumende kuwanisa vanhu dzidziso yakakwana pamusoro peEbola.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2471786' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voashona.com/a/zimbabwe-doctors/2471786.html' term='ebola'>
Vana Chiremba Voramwa Mabasa muZvipatara Zvikuru zveHurumende
WASHINGTON —
Kuratidzira kwavana chiremba, Junior Doctors, vemuzvipatara zvehurumende kwakatanga nepa Parirenyatwa Hospital neChina, kwapinda muzuva repiri.
Kuratidzira uku kunonzi kwapararirawo kuzvipatara zveHarare Hospital neMpilo Hospital kuBulawayo.
Vana chiremba ava vanoti vanoda kuti mari dzavari kutambira dziwedzerwe kubva pamadhora mazana masere kusvika pachiuru nemazana maviri.
Mazana masere emadhora aya anosanganisira mazana matatu emadhora semari yekubatsirikana padzimba dzekugara.
Vana chiremba ava vanotiwo havasi kubatwa zvakanaka nevakuru vepazvichipatara zvavanoshandira.
Nhengo yekomiti yeHospital Doctors Association, Dr Nyasha Mtetwa, vanoti vatora danho iri nokuti havasi kubatwa zvakanaka.
Studio7 haina kukwanisa kubata mukuru weParirenyatwa, Va Thomas Zigora, kanawo gurukota rezvehutano, Dr David Parirenyatwa, avo vange vasiri kudaira nharembozha yavo.
Asi vamwe mubazi rezvehutano vasina kuda kutaura mazita avo vanoti kana zvanetsa, hurumende ichatodaidza vana chiremba vechiuto kuzobatsira.
Pava kutyirwa kuti kuratidzira uku kunogona kukanganisa gadziriro yekudzivirira chirwere che Ebola icho chakonzeresa dambudziko guru kunyika dzekumawirira kweAfrica.
Zimbabwe kusvika pari zvino haina kana munhu mumwe chete ati abatwa nechirwere che Ebola, kunyange hayo iri kugara yakagadzirira zvemhando yepamusoro sezviri kuita nyika dzose dzepasi rino.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2478562' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voashona.com/a/zimbabwe-health/2478562.html' term='ebola'>
Hurumende Inoti Zimbabwe Haina Chirwere cheEbola
WASHINGTON —
Hurumende inoti veruzhinji havafanirwe kutya zvichitevera mashoko ekuti pane mudzidzi wepa Harare Polytechnic anobva ku Democratic Republic of Congo akachengetedzwa pa Wilkins Hospital muHarare mushure mekufungidzirwa kuti ane Ebola.
Gurukota rezvehutano, VaDavid Parirenyatwa, avo vashanyira chipatara ichi neChina vanoti mushure mekuongororwa, murwere uyu haana kuonekwa aine chirwere che Ebola, asi kuti ane malaria.
Asi VaParirenyatwa vatiwo vatumirawo ku South Africa zvakatorwa pamurwere uyu kuti zvinoongororwawo kana aine Ebola. Vatiwo chipatara cheWilkins hachisi kushandiswa neveruzhinji pari zvino kudzamara zvabuda pachena kuti chirwere cheyi chiri kunetsa mudzidzi uyu.
Mukuru webazi rezvehutano mukanzuru ye Harare, Dr Prosper Chonzi, vakaudzawo vatori venhau kuti murwere uyu anga achiongororwa kwemasvondo matatu ari kuchipatara Parirenyatwa, asi akatanga kurutsa neChitatu pamwe nekubuda ropa, izvo zvakaita kuti aendeswe kuWilkins.
Chirwere che Ebola chauraya vanhu vava kuda kusvika kuzviuru zvina, zvikuru muLiberia, Sierra Leone neGuinea.
Asi Dr Chonzi vanoti vanhu havafanire kutya nekuti hurumende yakagadzirira zvakasimba kurwisa Ebola ikapinda munyika.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2422445' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voashona.com/a/ebola-zimbabwe-parirenyatwa-africa/2422445.html' term='ebola'>
Zimbabwe Yoyambira Vanhu Kusashanyira Nyika Dzine Ebola
WASHINGTON —
Hurumende inoti vanhu vanofanirwa kumbomira kushanyira nyika dzemu West Africa dzakatarisana nedambudziko rechirwere che Ebola.
Nyika idzi dzinoti Liberia, Seirra Leone, Guine neNigeria.
Vachitaura neStudio7, gurukota rezvehutano, Doctor David Parirenyatwa, vati vari kukurudzira zvakasimba zvizvarwa zveZimbabwe kuti zvimbomira kushanyira nyika idzi.
VaParirenyatwa vanoti kunyange hazvo Zimbabwe yakagadzirira kurwisa chirwere ichi, zvizvara zveZimbabwe, kunyanya vanhu vanoshanyira nzvimbo dzinonamatirwa kuNigeria, vambomira kuita izvi kusvika pawanikwa nzira dzekurwisa chirwere ichi.
Doctor Parirenyatwa vanoti hurumende yakatotanga zvirongwa zvekuvhunzurudza vashanyi vanobva kunyika dzakatarisana nedambudziko iri pamwe nekuvavheneka kuitira kuti chirwere ichi chisapinzwe munyika nevashanyi.
Doctor Parirenyatwa vanotiwo chipatara che Wilkins Hospital uko kunorapwa vane zvirwere zvinotapuriranwa, ndicho chiri kushandiswa kuongorora avo vanenge vari kufungidzirwa kuti vangangove nechirwere ichi.
Doctor Parirenyatwa vanoti vanenge vafungidzirwa kuti vangangove nechirwere ichi vanoongororwa kwemazuva makumi maviri nerimwe kuitira kuti vaonekwe kuti vane hutachiwona hwechirwere ichi here kana kuti kwete.
Sangano re World Health Organisation, WHO, rinoti vanhu vanosvika chiuru nemazana maviri vaurayiwa nechirwere ichi mu West Africa.
WHO inotiwo huwandu hwevari kubatwa nechirwere ichi huri kuramba huchikwira.
</doc>
<doc id='voa_2452039' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voashona.com/a/zimbabwe-health/2452039.html' term='ebola'>
Zimbabwe Yotungamira SADC Kudzivirira Ebola
WASHINGTON —
Nyika dzemuAfrica nemasangano anopa rubatsiro anoti nyika dzakabudirira dzinofanira kuwedzera rubatsiro kunyika dzekumawirira kwe Africa dzawirwa nedambudziko nechirwere che Ebola.
Chirwere ichi chauraya vanhu zviuru zviviri nemazana mana pavanhu zviuru zvina nemazana manomwe vakabatwa nechirwere ichi.
Nyika dzabatwa nechirwere ichi dzinosanganisira Liberia, Guinea, Nigeria, Sierra Leone, Senegal neDemocratic Republic of Congo.
Bazi reUnited Nations rinoona nezvehutano, reWorld Health Organization, rinoti pari kudiwa mari inosvika bhiriyoni imwe chete yemadhora yekushandisa mukurwisa chirwere ichi.
Bazi iri rinoti chirwere ichi chakomba zvakanyanya pane zvarati ramboona munhoroondo yechirwere ichi.
Munyori mukuru wUnited Nations, VaBan Ki Moon, vari kutarisirwa neChina kuparurawo chirongwa chekutsvaga mari nerubatsiro rwekurwisa denda iri.
Mutungamiri weAmerica, VaBarack Obama, vanoti America yave kutumira mauto zviuru zvitatu kuLiberia kunobatsira kurwisa chirwere ichi.
America kusvika pari zvino yapa nyika idzi mari inosvika zana remamiriyoni emadhora.
Zvichakadaro, Zimbabwe inova sachigaro weSADC, ndiyo iri kutungamira hurongwa hwekurwisa Ebola mudunhu rekuchamhembe kweAfrica iri.
Gurukota rinoona nezvehutano, Dr David Parirenyatwa, vanoti vari kuyedza kugadzirira dunhu kubva kuchirwere ichi kunyange hazvo Democratic Republic of Congo yakawirwa nedambudziko iri.
</doc>
